      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例复制活动工作簿上的表格样式中的最后一个样式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> tableStyles = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyles</span>\n    tableStyles.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(tableStyles.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Duplicate</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;样式5&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例复制第一张工作簿中指定索引的表格样式，并显示复制样式的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> tableStyle = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">TableStyles</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Duplicate</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;样式三&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(tableStyle.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
